---

## 🎯 The Problem

Booking a health checkup is surprisingly hard:

- **For patients:** Calling clinics, explaining symptoms repeatedly, uncertain about which test to choose
- **For clinics:** Scattered enquiries across phone/email/WhatsApp, manual data entry, missed follow-ups

**Health Checkup Genius bridges this gap** — patients self-serve online, clinics get structured data in their workflow tools automatically.

---

## ✨ Key Features

| Feature | What It Does | PM Thinking Behind It |
|---------|-------------|----------------------|
| **Smart Test Selection** | Dropdown with 9 test types (Full Body, Blood Test, Diabetes, Thyroid, Heart, Liver, Kidney, Vitamin, Custom) | Reduces "which test do I need?" support calls |
| **Multi-Step Form** | 3-step flow: Personal Info → Test Details → Review & Submit | Reduces cognitive load; progress indicator increases completion rate |
| **Slot Preference** | Date picker + time slot selection (Morning/Evening) | Gives patients control, helps clinics plan capacity |
| **Auto-Generated Enquiry ID** | Unique ID format `HC-YYYYMMDD-XXX` | Traceability for both patient and clinic |
| **Instant Email Confirmation** | Patient receives acknowledgement within seconds of submission | Builds trust, reduces anxiety, sets expectations |
| **n8n Lead Automation** | Form data flows into Gmail + structured field mapping + admin CC | Zero manual data entry; clinic staff work in tools they already use |


